# HEV-BMS-Simulation

## Project Overview
This project focuses on the simulation of a Hybrid Electric Vehicle (HEV) Battery Management System (BMS) using MATLAB/Simulink and Python.

## Objectives
- State of Charge (SOC) Estimation
- State of Health (SOH) Monitoring
- Cell Balancing
- Thermal Analysis
- Overcharge and Over-discharge Protection
- Performance Evaluation

## Tools Used
- MATLAB
- Simulink
- Python
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- GitHub

## Project Structure
- Dataset
- MATLAB_Model
- Python_Code
- Results
- PPT

## Expected Outcomes
- Accurate SOC estimation
- Battery safety monitoring
- Improved battery efficiency
- Performance analysis under varying load conditions
